= TTF_FontDescent =

Get the offset from the baseline to the bottom of the font This is a negative value, relative to the baseline.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_FontDescent(const TTF_Font *font);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns font descent

